## 🔍 **Search Patterns**

### **Finding All References**
```bash
# Exact match (case-sensitive)
grep -r ExactName src/

# Case-insensitive
grep -ri name src/

# With line numbers
grep -rn ElementName src/

# Only in TypeScript files
grep -r ElementName src/ --include=*.ts

# Show context (3 lines before/after)
grep -rn -C 3 ElementName src/
```

### **Using Codebase Search**
```typescript
// For semantic understanding of usage
codebase_search({
  query: Where is MyInterface used?,
  target_directories: []
});
```

