# Step 2: Analyze usages
# - wallet.ts: Definition (to be removed last)
# - class.ts: Import (to be removed)
# - class.ts: Implementation (to be removed)

# Step 3: Remove usages first
# - Remove from import statement
# - Remove from implements clause

# Step 4: Remove definition
# - Delete interface from wallet.ts

# Step 5: Verify
$ bun run build
