## 🚀 **Quick Reference**

**Before removing any code:**
```bash
# 1. Search
grep -r CodeElement src/

# 2. Update usages
# (edit files that use the element)

# 3. Remove definition
# (delete the code element)

# 4. Verify
bun run build
```

**Remember: Search → Update → Remove → Verify**

This is a fundamental skill in refactoring. Master it, and your refactoring will be safe and professional.
